---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pricing" description="OpenCan is free to self-host forever under AGPL-3.0. A managed hosted plan is coming soon.">

  <section class="pt-24 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-[#111827] mb-4">
          Simple, honest pricing
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Self-host for free, forever. A managed hosted plan is on the way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Plans -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">

        <!-- Self-hosted plan -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border-2 border-[#2563EB] bg-white p-8 relative">
          <span class="absolute -top-3.5 left-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-[#2563EB] text-white shadow-sm">
            <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 0C5.374 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23A11.509 11.509 0 0112 5.803c1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576C20.566 21.797 24 17.3 24 12c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
            </svg>
            Open source · AGPL-3.0
          </span>

          <div class="mt-3">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#111827]">Self-hosted</h2>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#111827]">$0</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-lg">/ forever</span>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Your data, your server, your rules. Deploy the full stack with a single Docker Compose command. No seat pricing, no usage limits, no vendor lock-in.
            </p>
          </div>

          <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3">
            {[
              'Feedback boards with voting',
              'Public roadmap',
              'Changelog with email notifications',
              'Admin dashboard',
              'Embeddable in-app widget',
              'Full-text search',
              'Outbound webhooks (Slack, Linear)',
              'Guest posting support',
              'Unlimited boards',
              'Unlimited voters',
              'Google & GitHub OAuth',
              'Session revocation via Redis',
            ].map(feature => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#2563EB] shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                {feature}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>

          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/sriramgopalan/opencan"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-[#111827] text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors"
            >
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 0C5.374 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23A11.509 11.509 0 0112 5.803c1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576C20.566 21.797 24 17.3 24 12c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
              </svg>
              Get started on GitHub
            </a>
            <a
              href="/docs/self-hosting"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-[#111827] text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors"
            >
              Self-hosting guide
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Hosted plan (coming soon) -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 relative">
          <span class="absolute -top-3.5 left-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 border border-gray-200">
            Coming soon
          </span>

          <div class="mt-3">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#111827]">Hosted</h2>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <span class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#111827]">$?</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500 text-lg">/ mo</span>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-3 text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              We're working on a fully managed hosted plan — zero ops, automatic updates, and straightforward pricing. Sign up below to be first to know.
            </p>
          </div>

          <ul class="mt-8 space-y-3">
            {[
              'Everything in self-hosted',
              'Zero infrastructure to manage',
              'Automatic updates',
              'Managed backups',
              'Priority support',
            ].map(feature => (
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-500">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                {feature}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>

          <!-- Email capture -->
          <div class="mt-8">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#111827] mb-3">Get notified when it's ready</p>
            <form id="notify-form" class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <input
                id="notify-email"
                type="email"
                required
                placeholder="you@example.com"
                class="w-full px-3.5 py-2.5 text-sm rounded-lg border border-gray-200 bg-[#FAFAFA] text-[#111827] placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#2563EB] focus:border-transparent transition"
              />
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="w-full px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-[#2563EB] text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
              >
                Notify me
              </button>
            </form>
            <div id="notify-success" class="hidden mt-4 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-green-700 bg-green-50 border border-green-100 rounded-lg px-4 py-3">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              You're on the list. We'll reach out when the hosted plan is ready.
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-3">No spam. One email when it launches.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- FAQ / reassurance row -->
      <div class="mt-16 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center px-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#2563EB]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#111827] mb-1">Your data stays yours</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Self-hosting means your feedback data never touches our servers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center px-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#2563EB]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#111827] mb-1">No seat pricing, ever</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Invite your whole team. The self-hosted plan has no per-user cost.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center px-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-50 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#2563EB]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#111827] mb-1">Deploy in minutes</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Docker Compose brings up the full stack — app, Postgres, Redis, MinIO — in one command.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    const form = document.getElementById('notify-form') as HTMLFormElement | null;
    const success = document.getElementById('notify-success');

    form?.addEventListener('submit', e => {
      e.preventDefault();
      // Wire this up to your email collection service (Resend, Formspree, etc.)
      form.classList.add('hidden');
      success?.classList.remove('hidden');
    });
  </script>

</Layout>
